Biograd na Moru.title: Biograd na Moru
Biograd na Moru.byline: Biograd na Moru is a small, tourist city in Dalmatia, Croatia near Zadar.

Biogradska Gora National Park.title: Biogradska Gora National Park
Biogradska Gora National Park.byline: Biogradska Gora is in the Kolašin Municipality, in the northeastern part of Montenegro.
